                            strong.text-red PR: 
                            |  That’s a very good question. Obviously, it would have to be a color that you can use, I mean, not pea green. But it might even be pea green under certain conditions. But, all things being equal, the idea is less the 
                            em attribute 
                            | of red than it is the 
