                        p 
                            strong.text-red PR: 
                            |  Big business people are usually pretty definite. They don’t shilly-shally around. And I am very direct. But you never work with the Chief Executive of a large corporation in these design matters. The decision comes down through three other executives. There’s no way you can do anything about it, unless you want to go over their heads. 

