                        p 
                            strong.text-red PR: 
                            |  What it accomplishes, if it accomplishes anything, is to dramatize the parts of the body that make dance, and it does it in a way that’s unusual, unexpected and memorable. A photograph of a dancer is a million dancers, not memorable. But this one you won’t forget.

